data.description: Stunning Ranch on Beautifully Landscaped Over-sized .60 Ac Lot in Quiet Cul-de-sac. The Privacy this Home Offers Surpasses that of Neighboring Properties. A Southern Living Style Stone Front Porch Sets the Tone for this Lovely Home. Step Into the Spacious Front Entry Flanked by a Guest Room, Currently Used as a Dedicated Home Office with Double Doors. Notice the Warm Stained Hardwoods that Flow Throughout the Main Living Area and Lead to the Handsome Great Room with Cathedral Ceiling, Custom Built-ins and Stone Fireplace. Open Concept Dining Area. Warm Stained Cabinetry Highlight the Chef's Kitchen with Breakfast Bar, Ample Counter Space and a "To Die For" Walk-in Pantry. The "Show Stopper" for this Home is a Fabulous 3-Season Sun Room with Eze Breeze Vinyl Windows, Second Dining Area, Grilling Deck, Tons of Living Space and Stone Fireplace! All This Overlooks a Lush Private Wooded Lot! Back Yard is Fenced Making it Perfect for Pets and Kids. Sophisticated Master on Main with Double Trey Ceiling with Uplighting Leads to Master En Suite with Seperate Tile Shower and Soaking Tub and Separate His and Her Vanities! Head Down Stairs to a Fantastic Finished Terrace Level! Terrace Level Offers the Ideal Space to Relax with Friends and Family. Built-in Bar & Wine Area Make Entertaining Easy. Three Additional Guest Rooms with Full Bath for Overnight Lake Guests. Home Gym Could Function as 6th Bedroom/Bunk Room for Grandkids! Beautiful Stone Patio is Just Off the Terrace Level Living Area and Offers Complete Privacy from the Neighbors! AUSSUMABLE LOAN at 2.25%. Gated Lake & Golf Community. 24 Hr Security. Great Amenities!
